COVID-19 Status

As of 7:06AM PT today, over 1.4 million Canadians have tested positive for COVID-19. Sadly, 25.5 thousand have died.

In the last day, 276 new infections were reported and 1 deaths. This is trending downwards.

Fortunately, 23.7 million doses of the vaccine have been administered. For those 12 years and older, 65% have their 1st shot and 6.2% are fully vaccinated!

Vaccination is speeding up, but there are 2.4 million doses in the freezer. It currently takes ~10 days for new deliveries to get into arms. At the current rate, all Canadians aged 12+ should have the first dose by Jul-12 and fully vaccinated by Oct-04. There is no approved vaccine for children aged 11 or younger.
